MID_支援_アクア_アサマ_Ｃ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa............$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaAsama, you've been staring\nat me for some time now...$k$pIs there something you need?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaLady Aqua... There is something\nI would like to ask of you.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaHuh?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaYou play an especially pivotal\nrole within our forces.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Wh-where is this coming from?\nWhat do you mean by that?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaYou've gained everyone's trust,\nand also due to your position...$k$pIt falls upon you to lead all of us.$k$pYou're constantly devoting yourself to the\nreturn of peace to this world, aren't you?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa............$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|One would think that you were a flag\nof justice that keeps us all aligned.$k$pHowever...is there anything you keep\nconcealed behind that calm exterior?$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaAnything...concealed?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaYes... At most times, I sense\na dark, sullen heart within you...$k$pYou think of protecting the world,\nand you know that someday it will$k$peventually be safe.$k$pBut you're thinking on a much\nlarger scale than the rest of us.$k$pWell, I suppose you could say that I\nget the impression that you're like me.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|............$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|That's the sort of coldness I'm\nfeeling from you... But, am I right?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|Even if you are, I have no\nobligation to answer you.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wd$w0|$Wsアサマ|$WaMy, my... There she goes.$k
MID_支援_アクア_アサマ_Ｂ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Hello there, Lady Aqua.\nHow are you doing?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|I can see you're no less\nsuspicious than usual...$k$pWhat do you care of how I'm doing?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaMy, I've been found out.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|...Did you come to talk to me again?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|Yes. I'd like to know more about\nthe darkness within your heart.$k$pI may find it to even be similar to mine.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaI have no idea if I'm anything like you...$k$pBut if my heart happened to be as\nyou'd described, what would you do?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Why, of course I would look forward\nto telling the others about you.$k$pPeople's inner feelings are quite\ninteresting, you know. Hahaha...$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|I see... Do as you like.$k$pI've never had any intention of talking\nabout my feelings with you, anyway.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wd$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|Oh, please wait, Lady Aqua.$k\n$Wmアクア|7$w0|$Wsアクア|$WaWhat is it...?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|If I promised to keep quiet after\nlearning the truth...would you tell me?$k$pIf you will, I'll shut it away in my heart.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|............$k$pI would never agree to\nsomething that vague.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wd$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Haha... Fair enough, Lady Aqua...\nBut you're only making me more interested.$k
MID_支援_アクア_アサマ_Ａ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Why hello, Lady Aqua.\nHow are you doing today?$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|I would prefer it if you didn't ask\nabout things you don't care about.$k$pWhat you want to know about isn't\nhow I'm doing. It's more about my$k$pheart, isn't it?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|Not at all, I'm very much interested now.\nI'm wondering if your heart is doing well.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Huh?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I've been thinking...$k$pPerhaps the reason why you seem so cold,\nis because you've closed your heart away.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaWhat do you mean?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaWhat I mean is that the only thing\nthat's restricting you, is yourself.$k$pYou've completely emptied your heart.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaEmptied my heart...?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|Haven't you ever needed to express\nyour pain to others in times of trouble?$k$pI've heard that talking to others about\nyour problems is very comforting.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E通常,|Telling other people would be comforting...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaIt's one of the many\nteachings of the Buddha.$k$p$E笑,|Well...even though, I, myself\ndon't believe in that at all.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa............$k$p$E笑,|Hehehe... So, you're trying to get\nme to talk about my troubles?$k$pYou've given me quite the\nroundabout for saying so.$k$pYou should have said that\nfrom the beginning.$k$pSo that means...\nyou were worried about me?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|I suppose I could have...$k$pBut at first, you had such a\ndark expression on your face...$k$pIt probably would have\nonly made you irritated.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,|Are you trying to call me gloomy?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|No, no. As the teachings of the Buddha\nstate, one should always speak the truth.$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaI see... Then I'll also speak the truth.$k$p$E通常,|At first, I thought you\nwere nothing but a bother...$k$pBut now, I'm quite happy to hear\nthat you were worried about me.$k$pI'll try a bit harder to rely on others more.\n...Is that an acceptable answer?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Your expression has become so much\nbrighter, so I don't see why it isn't.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|Heehee... Thank you, Asama.$k
MID_支援_アクア_アサマ_Ｓ: $t1$Wmアクア|7$Wmアサマ|3$w0|$Wsアクア|$WaAsama, do you have a moment?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$WaWhat is it, Lady Aqua? Are you ready\nto speak about your heart with me?$k\n$Wsアクア|$WaWell, no... Not exactly.\nWill you listen to me?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|Anything, as long as it proves interesting.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑,|Heehee...$k$p$E怒,|I understand that I do\nseem cold to others...$k$pBut, my desire to protect this world\nand live on with everyone is real.$k$p$Eキメ,|I trust you, and everyone else...\nAnd I'll continue to do so.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,|Ahahaha! You really are quite interesting!$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Huh...?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,|I'd already known that from the beginning.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E怒,|B-but―\nYou said you...!$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,|I knew, but I enjoyed observing you to\nsee if you would keep acting like that.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$Eキメ,|............$k$p$E笑2,|I'm amazed... Heehee. But I suppose\nthat's just the kind of person you are.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E怒,|Ah, well... I can't just keep watching\nlike this. I've held on far past my limit.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E通常,|Held on?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,照|Yes. I'm tired of observing\nyou as just another person.$k$pI want to always be by your side,\nand I will continue to protect you.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E苦,|Wh-wh-wha...$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$Eキメ,照|I love you.$k$pYou seem so ephemeral, so fragile...\nand I can't continue to just watch.$k$p...I want to protect you from close by.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E通常,照|Asama... Thank you.$k$p$E笑,照|Since you insist on doing so...\nMay I go along with it?$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E通常,照|Well, I don't think I'll be going to\nchange my mind any time soon...$k$pSo you should do whatever you'd like.$k\n$Wsアクア|$Wa$E笑2,照|Heehee... There you go, again.$k$pIt feels nice to banter\nwith someone so casually.$k$pAsama... Thank you.\nPlease take good care of me.$k\n$Wsアサマ|$Wa$E笑,照|Yes. Please take care of\nme as well, Lady Aqua...$k
